OL,3,CParents protest after school rated
OL,4,Cinadequate
OL,6,FParents have held a protest outside a
OL,7,Fschool after a damning report from
OL,8,FOfsted rated it 'inadequate' in all
OL,9,Fareas.
OL,11,FDozens gathered in Ryeish Green,
OL,12,FReading, saying Anthem, the academy
OL,13,Ftrust that runs Oakbank, failed both
OL,14,Fits pupils and teachers.
OL,16,FFollowing the backlash, Anthem has now
OL,17,Fannounced it will step down and hand
OL,18,Fthe school over to another trust.
