OL,6,FThe protest had been arranged before
OL,7,Fthe announcement by Anthem but parents
OL,8,Fdecided to go ahead with it saying
OL,9,Fthey want Anthem held to account for
OL,10,Fthe failings at Oakbank.
OL,12,FParents said their issues lie not with
OL,13,Fthe school but squarely with Anthem
OL,14,Fand say the new trust must be able to
OL,15,Foffer support at a more local level.
OL,17,FOfsted's findings at Oakbank included
OL,18,Fsafeguarding arrangements, disrupted
OL,19,Flearning, and a high turnover of staff.
