OL,4,Cinadequate
OL,6,FMP Yuan Yang said: "I posed a question
OL,7,Fto the education standards minister,
OL,8,Fsaying there have been brilliant
OL,9,Ftrusts in our constituency that have
OL,10,Fdone really well for schools, but when
OL,11,Fit comes to failing trusts and failing
OL,12,Fmulti-academy trusts that have let
OL,13,Fdown parents not just in one school
OL,14,Fbut multiple schools, I think parents
OL,15,Fwant more accountability for that. "
