OL,6,FAnnouncing the handover, Mohsen Ojja,
OL,7,FCEO of Anthem Schools Trust, said: "At
OL,8,FAnthem, our goal will always be to do
OL,9,Fwhat is best for the young people we
OL,10,Fsupport, and this decision was made
OL,11,Fwith the school's students first and
OL,12,Fforemost in our minds.
