OL,6,F"A final decision about which multi-
OL,7,Facademy trust will take over the
OL,8,Frunning of the school will be made in
OL,9,FMarch. In the meantime, we look
OL,10,Fforward to working with our
OL,11,Fimprovement partner Greenshaw Learning
OL,12,FTrust, which shares our values and
OL,13,Fcommitment to providing the very best
OL,14,Feducation provision for students.
OL,16,FAs a short term intervention,
OL,17,FGreenshaw Learning Trust will oversee
OL,18,Fthe running of the school in
OL,19,Fpartnership with Anthem.
